WEBVTT

56:30.136 --> 56:32.597
Look at
what they've done to you.

56:32.680 --> 56:34.516
-
-Are you in any pain?

56:34.599 --> 56:36.935
Hmm. It's temporary.

56:38.061 --> 56:41.439
I rest easy knowing the man who did this

56:43.149 --> 56:44.401
suffered worse.

56:46.486 --> 56:50.031
-
-My children, how are they?

56:52.158 --> 56:55.578
-Santiago's started crawling.
-Oh.

56:56.329 --> 57:00.125
He'll probably be sprinting
by the time I get out of this place.

57:00.208 --> 57:01.418
Don't lose hope.
